Road Atlanta - A road course in Braselton, GA, USA.
The facility is utilized for a wide variety of events,
including professional and amateur sports car and motorcycle races,
racing and driving schools, corporate programs and
testing for motorsports teams.
The track has 12 turns, including the famous "esses" between turns
three and five, and Turn 12, a downhill, diving turn.
The track is the home to Petit Le Mans, as well as AMA motorcycle racing.

